{
  "stem": "22685.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Tashkent is is in Uzbekistan.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We tried to, in the meantime, also, to cross the border to Iran, from there to Israel, because some people succeeded.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we were caught.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were lucky that we could escape.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so this was in '42, and '43, so we started to move to-- closer to Russia, and we came to [NON-ENGLISH], I got sick in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was-- and I ended up in a working battalion.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They had military army, and they had working army-- since I was a Polish citizen, still, originally.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they sent us to working battalions.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I worked in a factory, which made their own mines.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I ended up to work in the-- in the poice, in the military police of the factory.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Since while I was in college, I had a good experience in the basis of communism, because in every military group, there was a political agitator.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But our political agitator was a drunkard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he gave me-- so he found out that I know-- I'm familiar with the-- with those things, that I used to substitute.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And once I made a joke about Stalin, and I was arrested next day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When they took me from my--from the-- our factory was out of town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Took me-- they had to take me down-- well, they had the secret police to take me to their quarters-- headquarters.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went to the toilet, and I jumped from the window from the toilet.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I jumped out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I still have signs here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I schlepped myself to a village, and people were nice people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I knew people in that village, and I was a few days recuperating.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And here comes in another little thing I would think is fate.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
